# List of basic functions

| name | symbol |
|------|--------|
| buf  | `1`    |
| inv  | `~`    |
| eq   | `=`    |
| and  | `&`    |
| nand | `~&`   |
| or   | `|`    |
| nor  | `~|`   |
| xor  | `^`    |
| xnor | `~^`   |
| add  | `+`    |
| mul  | `*`    |

## structure

```js
[and, a, b, [or, c, [not, d]]]
```
